title: Acense Professional Large Chopping Board Catering Food Prep Cutting Colour Coded (Green)
features: Large Surface: Chopping anything is the most crucial part of cooking. You can’t do that in a corner! This is the reason why we have this Professional Large Chopping Board. This is one to promote the luxury of cooking and the ease of management.
Premium Quality: This large chopping pad is here to avoid spills and a strong base facilitates easy chopping and cutting. As for cleaning, the board can be easily washed using warm and soapy water.

Satisfaction guarantee: The items are 100% new and shipped by Acense from the for complete customer satisfaction. If you are not satisfied with the product, you can return it within 30 days from the purchase date.
Sturdy: The sturdy composition of this pad promotes stability while chopping and cutting. Moreover, it is lightweight and can be carried around in your layer without any fuss!
Classy Look: This Chopping Board is designed to make your cooking space neat and sophisticated and the thick plastic of this board makes it dishwasher friendly.
